\pard{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf2\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 Confidentiality: Preserving authorized restrictions on information\f1\lang2057  \f0\lang9 access and disclosure.\par
{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}Integrity: Guarding against improper information modification or\f1\lang2057  \f0\lang9 destruction.\par
