\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b B. The Stuxnet Worm\par
\b0 What happened: A highly sophisticated computer worm designed\f1\lang2057  \f0\lang9 not just to steal information, but to cause physical damage. It\f1\lang2057  \f0\lang9 specifically targeted the control systems of\f1\lang2057  \f0\lang9 Iranian nuclear\f1\lang2057  \f0\lang9 centrifuges, causing them to subtly malfunction and destroy\f1\lang2057  \f0\lang9 themselves.\par

\pard{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf2\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 Most significantly compromised CIA Triad - Integrity\par
{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}Why? - Worm caused physical damage to control systems\par
{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}Secondary Impacts - Confidentiality, the worm also stole information of the Iranian nuclear centrifuges\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\ul\f1\lang2057 In depth analysis on the Stuxnet Wrom:\ulnone\f0\lang9\par
The most significantly compromised CIA triad was definetaly integriry, as it involved specifically targeting supervisory control and data acquisition systems, \f1\lang2057  \f0\lang9 physically causing damage within them.\par
Installed by an Iranian engineer, the worm was physically brought into the facility, and injected using a USB drive, allowing the worm to get direct access to the system including ones not connected to the internet. \par
It stayed undetected with the help of a multiple advanced techniques such as man in the middle attacks that faked sensor signals to make infected systems appear to operate normally. Additionally the worm remained mostly dorment from late 2009 to 2010, allowing it to steal tageted information before conditions are met to excecute the payload, compromising another part of the CIA triad, confidentiality as it the worm was capable\f1\lang2057  \f0\lang9 of stealing sensitive data from the Iranian nuclear centrifuges. The targeted approach further limiting its visibility to broader networks, keeping it hidden longer. \par
When\f1\lang2057  \f0\lang9 the right conditions where met, the worm manipulated the operating system speeds of the centrifuges, causing them to fail and degrade faster than normal. It did this through exploiting zero day vulnarabilities in Siemens software controlling these systems\par
